+## Agent 12 ‚Äî Final Review and Cleanup (completed)
+
+### What was done
+
+**Cleanup:**
+1. **Removed `src/utils/callback-registry.ts`** ‚Äî dead code since Agent 1 unified all event handling through EventBus. No imports or exports referenced it.
+
+**Review verified:**
